                h2.project-details-headline Premier Fort Beach
            .col-10.project-details-headline-col.p-0.text-start
                div.project-details-text Welcome to Premier Fort Beach Hotel – Your Ideal Family Getaway!
                div.project-details-text Discover the perfect blend of comfort and excitement at Premier Fort Beach Hotel, a delightful 4-star paradise tailored for families with kids. Our resort is renowned for its exceptional offerings, ensuring an unforgettable experience for guests of all ages.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Accommodations for Every Need
                div.project-details-text Whether you’re planning a short escape or a longer stay, Premier Fort Beach Hotel offers a range of apartment options from cozy studios to spacious 3-bedroom apartments. Each accommodation is thoughtfully designed to provide a home away from home, ensuring comfort and convenience throughout your stay.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Family-Friendly Paradise
                div.project-details-text Our resort is a paradise for families, featuring two freshwater swimming pools, a dedicated children’s swimming pool, and two exhilarating water slides. Let the little ones explore the children’s playground and participate in our fantastic animation program, offering endless fun and excitement.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Culinary Delights
                div.project-details-text Indulge in a culinary journey at Premier Fort Beach Hotel. From fine dining experiences to a variety of restaurants on the resort, our diverse culinary offerings cater to every taste. Enjoy a gastronomic adventure with delicious meals prepared by our talented chefs.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Recreation and Wellness
                div.project-details-text Stay active and relaxed with our outdoor gym, table tennis or volleyball on the beach. For a more serene experience, visit our spa and wellness area, offering massages, beauty treatments, and more.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Convenience at Your Fingertips
                div.project-details-text Our 24-hour reception is here to assist you with information about various excursions, ensuring you make the most of your stay. Explore the surrounding area or embark on exciting adventures with the guidance of our knowledgeable staff.
                div.project-details-text Premier Fort Beach Hotel is not just a destination; it’s an experience designed to create lasting memories for you and your loved ones. Book your stay now and immerse yourself in the perfect blend of family-friendly fun, exquisite dining, and relaxation!
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Area & Beach
                div.project-details-text Premier Fort Apart Hotel is a heaven nestled along the pristine coastline, offering an idyllic escape where the beauty of the area seamlessly blends with the comforts of a luxurious resort. Situated right on the beach, this paradise provides a perfect backdrop for a delightful and rejuvenating holiday experience.
                div.project-details-text It’s a destination where the beauty of the beach harmonizes with a plethora of amenities, promising an unforgettable and relaxing holiday for every guest.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Swimming Pools
                div.project-details-text The resort boasts an array of facilities and activities that cater to the diverse needs of its guests. Immerse yourself in the refreshing embrace of two crystal-clear freshwater swimming pools, each inviting you to bask in the warmth of the sun while enjoying the soothing sounds of the nearby waves. Families can delight in the specially designed children’s swimming pool, ensuring that every member of the family can create cherished memories in a safe and enjoyable environment.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Spa & Wellness
                div.project-details-text Indulge your senses in the wellness area, where tranquility and relaxation take center stage. Rejuvenate your body and mind with a variety of treatments, from invigorating massages to pampering sessions at the beauty salon and hairdresser. The on-site shops provide a convenient avenue for guests to pick up souvenirs or any essentials they may need during their stay.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Sport & Activities
                div.project-details-text The resort boasts an array of facilities and activities that cater to the diverse needs of its guests. Immerse yourself in the refreshing embrace of two crystal-clear freshwater swimming pools, each inviting you to bask in the warmth of the sun while enjoying the soothing sounds of the nearby waves. Families can delight in the specially designed children’s swimming pool, ensuring that every member of the family can create cherished memories in a safe and enjoyable environment.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Animation Program
                div.project-details-text For the little ones, a vibrant children’s playground awaits, filled with laughter and the joy of carefree play. Adventure seekers can revel in the excitement of two thrilling water slides, providing an exhilarating way to cool off and add an extra dose of fun to the sunny days. Fitness enthusiasts will find their haven in the outdoor gym, allowing them to stay active while surrounded by the breathtaking views of the beach.
                div.project-detail-img-container.d-flex.justify-content-center   
                    img.project-details-img(src='https://dirabulgaritbucket.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/green-fort-suites/1744367105500-green-fort-suites-building-plan.webp' alt='Building plans of Premier Fort Beach')
                div.project-details-text.text-center <i>Premier Fort Beach building plans</i>
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Great Investment
                div.project-details-text You can purchase an apartment in the best complex on the Bulgarian Black Sea coast right by the sea. An apartment in Premier Fort will be your family’s favorite vacation place in Bulgaria and a perfect investment for you. Apartments from 65 000 to 650 000 euro, from a cozy studios to a luxurious 3-bedroom apartments.
                div.project-details-text The Owners of apartments in the complex are paying the following annual fees and taxes:
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>●</strong> Maintenance and management fee in amount of 21 euro including 20% VAT, per one square meter of the build up area.
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>●</strong> Annual tax in amount of 278 euro including VAT 20%, for internet and television connection and maintenance of the access key-cards.
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>●</strong> Insurance – 50 euro for a studio apartment, 60 euro for a 1-bedroom apartment and 70 euro for a 2-bedroom and 85 eur for a 3-bedroom apartment.
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>●</strong> Fee for servicing the utility bills in amount of 30 euro.
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>●</strong> Real estate and garbage tax can be paid by our company at the same rates as of the Nessebar municipality.
                div.project-details-text There are no additional taxes for general repairs and renovations of the buildings and the constructions on the territory of the complex, everything is included into the sale price.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Project Properties
                div.project-details-text All apartments are fully furnished, absolutely ready for living and renting in accordance with the tour operators standards and requirements.
                div.project-details-text The finishing works in all apartments were carried out using only high quality materials.
                div.project-details-text The Complex is designed for year-round living.
                div.project-details-text The construction is monolithic using the modern technology of “dry” construction with high quality materials. The masonry of the walls /including the internal ones/ is laid with bricks or aerated concrete, an environmentally friendly materials with excellent technical specifications. The internal walls and ceilings are sheathed with plasterboard.
                div.project-details-text &nbsp<strong>● Entrance hall and kitchen box:</strong> Floor – ceramic floor tiles, walls and ceiling – latex paint.
